nique structure which had close connection to\nthe magnetic solar cycle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2022 14:19:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 1 Jan 2023 13:12:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-07"}
