otstep planning algorithm\nwith all of these features into the mapping algorithm and the walking algorithm\nto solve the navigation problem is validated with simulation and real robot.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2022 02:28:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-11"}
